# Page not loading

## User issue
The page is not loading.

## Possible causes
- Slow or unstable internet connection
- Frontend rendering issue
- API request failure
- Server-side issue
- Browser incompatibility

## Troubleshooting steps
1. Ask the user to check their internet connection and refresh the page.
2. Ask the user to try opening the page in a different browser.
3. Check the console for errors or failed requests.
4. Verify if data from the API is loading correctly.

## User-friendly response
Please make sure your internet connection is stable while using the website. 

You can also try opening the page in a different browser. 

If the issue persists, please let us know which page it occurs on and whether you see any error messages so we can investigate further. 

## Internal note
The issue may be related to browser incompatibility, frontend rendering problems, Api failures, or server-side issues.
